0-05-04-upload.png 1180w,\n/static/996b4f8a5056232f20e6301462f4e8e1/b30aa/2020-05-04-upload.png 1405w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/996b4f8a5056232f20e6301462f4e8e1/fcda8/2020-05-04-upload.png\"\n          alt=\"Tech support!\"\n          title=\"Tech support!\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Tech support!</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Nanthan 在一场车祸之后被自己的白富美女友将自己的意识上传至网上，在虚拟世界 Nanthan 爱上了自己的服务人员，并意识到自己的死亡可能是一场阴谋。</p>\n<p>这不是一个烧脑剧，逻辑上有很多纰漏，角色也有点脸谱化，演员可能故意演得很生硬使得这个剧更加轻喜剧化，虽然讲的是谋杀但整个看起来很轻松，值得一看。</p>\n<p>May the 4th be with you.</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"tv"},"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2020/05/04/Upload科幻喜剧，这个可以.html","date":"May 04, 2020","title":"Upload科幻喜剧，这个可以"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tv/2020/05/04/Upload科幻喜剧，这个可以.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/05/04/从RN到Flutter-从Dart开始.html","title":"从RN到Flutter-从Dart开始"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2020/05/05/凑数的西部世界第三季.html","title":"凑数的西部世界第三季"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tv"}}}}}